OL,3,CResearchers look to uncover impact of
OL,4,Cplastic waste on Antarctica
OL,6,FResearchers in Hampshire are looking
OL,7,Fto uncover the damage that plastic
OL,8,Fwaste is having on Antarctica.
OL,10,FThe work is being carried out by
OL,11,FPortsmouth University in an effort to
OL,12,Fpreserve what the researchers describe
OL,13,Fas "one of the world's most fragile
OL,14,Fenvironments".
OL,16,FThe team were aboard polar research
OL,17,Fvessel HMS Protector, collaborating
OL,18,Fwith the Royal Navy to carry out their
OL,19,Ftests.
