OL,3,CResearchers look to uncover impact of
OL,4,Cplastic waste on Antarctica
OL,6,FThey used a drone to survey the
OL,7,FAntarctic coastline and pinpoint areas
OL,8,Fwhere litter has washed up.
OL,10,FWater samples and marine sediments
OL,11,Fhave been taken to measure the human
OL,12,Fimpact, especially through tourism, on
OL,13,Fthe frozen continent.
OL,15,FDr Keiron Roberts, a senior lecturer
OL,16,Fin sustainability and the built
OL,17,Fenvironment, and a member of the
OL,18,FRevolution Plastics Institute said:
OL,19,F"Coming from a navy family, being on
OL,20,Fboard HMS Protector has been a bucket-
OL,21,Flist experience.
