OL,3,CResearchers look to uncover impact of
OL,4,Cplastic waste on Antarctica
OL,6,F"The crew's support has been
OL,7,Fincredible, and this time among them
OL,8,Fis something I'll treasure forever.
OL,10,F"Without the crew of HMS Protector
OL,11,Fthis valuable data would not be
OL,12,Fpossible to collect.
OL,14,F"With their help we are now building
OL,15,Fup an evidence base of the impacts
OL,16,Fthat humans are having in the region,
OL,17,Fparticularly microplastics, and hope
OL,18,Fto continue this work with them moving
OL,19,Fforward."
