OL,3,CResearchers look to uncover impact of
OL,4,Cplastic waste on Antarctica
OL,6,FDr Adele Julier, a senior lecturer and
OL,7,Fpalaeoecologist, is looking at climate
OL,8,Fand weather changes across Antarctic
OL,9,Fand said: "Setting pollen slides
OL,10,Faround the ship and counting pollen
OL,11,Fevery day at a microscope in the
OL,12,Fwarfare room has been a surreal and
OL,13,Ffascinating experience.
OL,15,F"The crew have all been so welcoming
OL,16,Fand friendly, and have put up
OL,17,Fadmirably with me getting way too
OL,18,Fexcited about finding moss."
