OL,3,CResearchers look to uncover impact of
OL,4,Cplastic waste on Antarctica
OL,6,FThe United Nations estimates that more
OL,7,Fthan eight million metric tonnes of
OL,8,Fplastic enter the planet's oceans
OL,9,Fevery year.
OL,11,FThe two scientists will now analyse
OL,12,Fthe results of their studies at their
OL,13,Flaboratories in Portsmouth.
OL,15,FMeanwhile HMS Protector is now headed
OL,16,Ffor Punta Arenas at the southern tip
OL,17,Fof Chile for a rotation of some of her
OL,18,Fcrew with colleagues from back in the
OL,19,FUK as she prepares for the next phase
OL,20,Fof her Antarctic deployment.
